latestIgtvVideos.title: 5-minute super-easy makeup tutorial !! ☺️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A quick, easy, beginner friendly five-minute makeup transformation from homeless to glam using only 5  affordable products ( No foundation or CONTOURING or brushes) !! 😜
.
.
Just perfect if you are bored or feeling a little dull in your pyjamas all day long or want to do a quick glam before that video calling session with your buddies/family 🙋
.
.
Product Details : .
.
▶️ Eyebrows : Miss Claire eyebrow cake ( you can use any brown/ dark brown eyeshadow to fill in your brows with any eyebrow brush) .
▶️ Maybelline Fit Me Concealer : You can use any Concealer and use it lightly/heavily to cover dark circles/ pigmentation
.
▶️Lakme Iconic Kajal : Use it as both kajal and eyeliner
.
▶️Swiss beauty lash extension Mascara : You can use any mascara you have.
.
▶️ Lipstick : The Body shop matte lip liquid in Goa Magnolia 026 ( You can use any lipstick shade of your choice )
.
.
🌺Tip : Use your lipstick as a blush and an eyeshadow to add some colour to your cheeks and eyelids---> makes a huge difference, trust me ☺️ !! .
.
.
❤️Please like and share and do comment and tag me if you try this❤️ !! 😇
.
.
